<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FastPay | Mini Wallet</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">FastPay</p>
          <h1 class="page-title">A faster mini wallet experience for transfers, wallets, and history.</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">Manage wallets, submit transfers, and review transaction history with a clean, modern FastPay interface.</p>
          <div class="page-actions">
            <a href="/viewwallets" class="button">View Wallets</a>
            <a href="/createtransfer" class="button">Create Transfer</a>
            <a href="/transactionhistory" class="button">View History</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-card">
          <h2>FastPay overview</h2>
          <p>Everything stays the same under the hood — your wallet and transfer logic are untouched. This release only refreshes the UI with a premium dark banking theme.</p>
          <ul class="summary-list">
            <li><strong>Brand new styling.</strong> More polished tables, cards, buttons, and spacing.</li>
            <li><strong>Better readability.</strong> Clear labels, strong contrast, and friendly form layout.</li>
            <li><strong>FastPay identity.</strong> A modern financial dashboard feel without changing features.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>